<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1428795-ray-is-arrested-in-1985-and-goes-to">Ray is arrested in 1985 and goes to prison. In order to &#39;escape&#39; the despair he starts daydreaming. In one dream he marries Halle Berry. Halle Berry only became famous in the 90&#39;s, after being crowned Miss Ohio in 1986. The dead row prisoners are not allowed to watch TV or read magazines. Someone please explain?</a>
</div>
