    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2563000969" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2563000969" />
    <a title="Syl Sabastian" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/48422533-syl-sabastian"><img alt="Syl Sabastian" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1520059100p2/48422533.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2563000969?book_show_action=true">Oct 15, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Syl Sabastian" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Syl Sabastian" href="/user/show/48422533-syl-sabastian">Syl Sabastian</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2563000969" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8199384314979786521">A powerful, emotional read. It&apos;s not every day we get to see life from a side we wouldn&apos;t ordinarily know. Experiencing the unimaginable is powerful because we tend to not believe what we can&apos;t imagine. When we do, and we know what we didn&apos;t before, we can&apos;t undo such knowing. Awareness is powerful, as is Understanding, both which don&apos;t always come easy. This amazing story, well delivered, adds to us human beings, providing a Perspective on the human condition which extends us as people. &quot;The mo</span>
  <span id="freeText8199384314979786521" style="display:none">A powerful, emotional read. It's not every day we get to see life from a side we wouldn't ordinarily know. Experiencing the unimaginable is powerful because we tend to not believe what we can't imagine. When we do, and we know what we didn't before, we can't undo such knowing. Awareness is powerful, as is Understanding, both which don't always come easy. This amazing story, well delivered, adds to us human beings, providing a Perspective on the human condition which extends us as people. "The moment we treat others as less than human, that's the moment we become monsters." A quote which comes to mind for me to represent a deep Understanding from the book. A sharing of intimacy-of-being well worth reading.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8199384314979786521" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


