      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/17022329.Anthony_Ray_Hinton">About Anthony Ray Hinton</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/17022329.Anthony_Ray_Hinton"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1509476006p3/17022329.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/17022329.Anthony_Ray_Hinton">Anthony Ray Hinton
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
541
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer7750105027905954811"><b>Anthony Ray Hinton</b> spent nearly thirty years on death row for crimes he didn’t commit. Released in April 2015, Hinton now speaks widely on prison reform and the power of faith and forgiveness. He lives in Alabama.</span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

